org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util

Class LauncherSecurityManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.SecurityManager
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.LauncherSecurityManager

  • public class LauncherSecurityManager
extends SecurityManager
    class for masquerading System.exit(int). Use for test main method with System.exit(int ) usage: new LauncherSecurityManager(); try { CellCounter.main(args); fail("should be exception"); } catch (SecurityException e) { assert(.,e.getExitCode()); }
